### OSS 对象存储接口调试
### 使用方式：IDEA HTTP Client 中点击左侧绿色箭头运行

### 基础地址（Gateway）
@baseUrl = http://localhost:1000/api/oss

### ========== 1. 签发上传凭证 ==========
### POST /api/oss/policy
### 前端上传前先调用此接口获取 Presigned PUT URL

POST {{baseUrl}}/policy
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "bucket": "mall-product",
    "businessType": "spu",
    "contentType": "image/jpeg",
    "fileSize": 1048576,
    "originalFilename": "product-photo.jpg"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("uploadId", response.body.data.uploadId);
    client.global.set("uploadUrl", response.body.data.uploadUrl);
    client.global.set("objectName", response.body.data.objectName);
    client.global.set("bucket", response.body.data.bucket);
    client.log("uploadId: " + response.body.data.uploadId);
    client.log("uploadUrl: " + response.body.data.uploadUrl);
%}

### ========== 2. 前端直传（模拟） ==========
### PUT uploadUrl（文件二进制直接传到 MinIO）
### 注意：此请求需要 MinIO 运行才能成功，手动在浏览器/Postman 中测试
###
### curl -X PUT "{{uploadUrl}}" \
###   -H "Content-Type: image/jpeg" \
###   --data-binary @product-photo.jpg

### ========== 3. 上传完成回调 ==========
### POST /api/oss/callback
### 前端上传到 MinIO 成功后调用，写入元数据到 DB

POST {{baseUrl}}/callback
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "uploadId": "{{uploadId}}",
    "bucket": "{{bucket}}",
    "objectName": "{{objectName}}"
}

### ========== 4. 获取下载 URL（私有文件） ==========
### GET /api/oss/download-url

GET {{baseUrl}}/download-url?bucket=mall-private&objectName=import/2026/06/23/test.xlsx

### ========== 5. 删除文件 ==========
### DELETE /api/oss/file

DELETE {{baseUrl}}/file?bucket={{bucket}}&objectName={{objectName}}

### ========== 6. 参数校验测试 ==========

### 6.1 Bucket 不在白名单
POST {{baseUrl}}/policy
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "bucket": "evil-bucket",
    "businessType": "spu",
    "contentType": "image/jpeg",
    "fileSize": 1048576,
    "originalFilename": "hack.exe"
}

### 6.2 文件类型不允许
POST {{baseUrl}}/policy
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "bucket": "mall-product",
    "businessType": "spu",
    "contentType": "application/x-msdownload",
    "fileSize": 1048576,
    "originalFilename": "virus.exe"
}

### 6.3 文件超过大小限制（> 10MB 图片）
POST {{baseUrl}}/policy
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "bucket": "mall-product",
    "businessType": "spu",
    "contentType": "image/jpeg",
    "fileSize": 20971520,
    "originalFilename": "huge-photo.jpg"
}

### 6.4 缺少必填字段
POST {{baseUrl}}/policy
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "bucket": "mall-product"
}
